{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_10_01_short",
  "title": "赤崎こころ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、こころ。最近、今まで以上に頑張ってるな\n現場が一緒だった仕事相手の人達も、褒めてたぞ",
      "startTime": 9.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。こころは謙虚ですから\nBIG4になったからって、調子に乗ったりしません",
      "startTime": 16.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "偉くなった途端に態度を変えて、評判を下げる\n……そんな小物ムーブ、こころがすると思いますか？",
      "startTime": 23.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うん、それもそうだな……\nじゃあ、学校生活の方はどうなんだ？　勉強とか",
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですか急に。勉強……は、まぁ、それなりです\n大丈夫、じゃないかと思いますよ？　多分……",
      "startTime": 41.5398851395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "怪しいぞ。BIG4になって仕事が大幅に増えたろ？\n学校に行けない日が増えてるし、気になってな",
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こころの仕事を\n少しセーブした方がいいんじゃないかと思ってるんだ",
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}